value.0: Detailed carvings cover the surface of this finely-crafted door. The handiwork is of high quality and no doubt came at quite an expense.
Bloodstains and arcane markings cover the surface of this heavy stone door.

This stone alter has been used in countless bloodletting ceremonies as evidenced by the smattering of blood around it.  Who knows what form of torture has been inflicted during the sermons given here...
Upon closer glance, for some reason, this mirror is facing the wrong direction.
